Class Staff

Employee
Staff
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class Staff extends Employee implements IActionable, Serializable
This class represents a Staff of a branch. A staff has information such as name, role (Staff), gender, age, Account object and Branch.

    • displayNewOrders

      public void displayNewOrders()

      See Also:
      • Branch.getOrders()

    • viewOrder

      public void viewOrder()
      Staff is able to view a specific order based on Order ID. Method first asks for order ID. If valid, method will print out details of the order.

    • processOrder

      public void processOrder()
      Staff is able to process the order, preparing it for pickup. Method changes order status of an order from NEW to READY.

    • chooseAction
